ceive marketing messages from Uber. \u003Ca href=\"\u002Flegal\u002Fprivacy\u002Fdrivers-us\u002F\"\u003EPrivacy Statement\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","contact-collection.submit_button":"Next","content-positioning.add_vehicles_and_drivers.description":"Get started! To get fully activated, you will need to provide driver and vehicles details on the platform. You will be guided along the way and will know exactly what documents are needed at each step of your journey.","content-positioning.add_vehicles_and_drivers.headline":"Add vehicles and drivers.","content-positioning.be_an_entrepreneur.description":"At Uber, we want to empower you to be the best at what you do and help you grow as a Fleet Partner. Well help you every step of the way to fulfill your entrepreneurial aspirations from starting a business to efficiently managing one, irrespective of how small or large your fleet is.","content-positioning.be_an_entrepreneur.headline":"Be an entrepreneur","content-positioning.community.description.ubermilitary":"As a verified UberMILITARY member youll have access to exclusive deals in your city.","content-positioning.community.headline.ubermilitary":"Join our community","content-positioning.commute1.description":"It's tough to keep tabs on your commuting expenses. Parking. Gas. The occasional oil change. But it all adds up. Commute is an easy way to help cover those costs. Picking up a neighbor typically takes less than 10 minutes. And it's always worth your time.","content-positioning.commute1.headline":"Get up to $20 a day","content-positioning.commute2.description":"Youre in total control of the daysand directionsthat you pick up another commuter. Pick up a commuter only on your way to work or only on Tuesdays, its up to you.","content-positioning.commute2.headline":"Give rides on your schedule","content-positioning.commute3.description":"Sure, it makes economic sense to share the ride. But it also feels pretty good to help someone out. That empty seat youre filling means one less car is on the road.","content-positioning.commute3.headline":"Help your community","content-positioning.earn.description":"You can drive and earn as much as you want. And, the more you drive, the more youll make. Plus, youll get paid weekly and your fares get automatically deposited.","content-positioning.earn.description.freight":"Haul as much as you want and book loads right from the app. Prices are fair and there's no haggling with brokers. Start driving with UberFreight today.","content-positioning.earn.description.integrated":"Driving with Uber is your way to earn extra money anytime. And with more riders and trips than any other service, theres more money around every corner.","content-positioning.earn.description.intl":"You can drive and make as much as you want. And, the more you drive, the more you could make. Plus, your fares get automatically deposited weekly.","content-positioning.earn.description.ubermilitary":"Youre in charge when you drive with Uber. Theres no office and no boss. Work toward goals that matter to you, and stop when you need to.","content-positioning.earn.headline":"Make great money","content-positioning.earn.headline.integrated":"Make money with your car","content-positioning.earn.headline.ubermilitary":"Start earning more","content-positioning.easy.description":"Sign up today and youll be on the road in no time. Plus, signing up takes less than 4 minutes. Dont wait to start making great money with your car.","content-positioning.easy.description.freight":"Sign up today and youll be on the road in no time. Dont wait to start making great money with UberFreight.","content-positioning.easy.description.integrated":"Now with Instant Pay you can transfer your earnings to your bank account immediately. Theres no minimum withdrawal amount and you can cash out up to 5 times a day.**","content-positioning.easy.headline":"Signing up is easy","content-positioning.easy.headline.integrated":"Get paid instantly","content-positioning.easy.headline.integrated.variant":"Turn everyday into payday","content-positioning.flexibility.description":"Only drive when it works for you. Theres no office and no boss. That means youll always start and stop on your timebecause with Uber, youre in charge.","content-positioning.flexibility.description.freight":"When you complete a load, the payment goes straight into your bank account. Never again wait 30 days for payment.","content-positioning.flexibility.description.integrated":"Uber is a fun, new way to make extra money that works around your schedule and current job. Drive anytime, as much or as little as you wantits up to you.","content-positioning.flexibility.description.ubermilitary":"Whether youre active military, a veteran, or a military family member, you can make driving work for your schedule. Drive for a few trips or a few hours.","content-positioning.flexibility.description.variant":"Uber is a fun, new way to make extra money that works around your schedule and current job. Drive anytime, as much or as little as you wantits up to you.","content-positioning.flexibility.headline":"Set your own schedule","content-positioning.flexibility.headline.freight":"Get paid right away","content-positioning.flexibility.headline.integrated":"Choose when to drive","content-positioning.flexibility.headline.variant":"Choose when to drive","content-positioning.flexible_schedule.description":"Take trips for a few hours in the mornings, every night, or just on weekendsit's up to you. You are your own boss and you can choose when and how much you work.","content-positioning.flexible_schedule.headline":"Work on your schedule","content-positioning.good_money.description":"You'll make money by bringing people the things they love. Between deliveries, it's just you. So bump your favorite tunes and enjoy cruising around your city.","content-positioning.good_money.headline":"Earn good money","content-positioning.headline":"Drive when you want","content-positioning.headline.commute":"Join the community, and share your way to work","content-positioning.headline.delivery":"A new way to","content-positioning.headline.fleet":"How to get started?","content-positioning.headline.ubermilitary":"The freedom to earn more","content-positioning.instantpay.description":"Now with Instant Pay you can transfer your earnings to your bank account immediately. Theres no minimum withdrawal amount and you can cash out up to 5 times a day.**","content-positioning.instantpay.headline.variant1":"Get paid instantly","content-positioning.instantpay.headline.variant2":"Turn everyday into payday","content-positioning.management_tools.description":"Grow your business in a sustainable way by getting access to powerful tools online that help you do more,  like the UberFLEET App and Fleet Web Dashboard. Our tools are for everyone - whether you own 1, 5 or 100 cars.","content-positioning.management_tools.headline":"Smart management tools","content-positioning.no_driver_no_problem.description":"You can still partner with Uber. Discover offline options available in your city to find driver partners who meet your requirements.","content-positioning.no_driver_no_problem.headline":"No driver? No problem","content-positioning.personal_vehicle.description":"Depending on the rules in your city, you may be able to deliver with your car, bike or scooter. Handle the wheel and well handle the rest.","content-positioning.personal_vehicle.headline":"Choose your wheels","content-positioning.safety.description":"Uber is dedicated to keeping people safe on the road. Our technology enables us to focus on driver safety before, during, and after every trip.","content-positioning.safety.headline":"Safety behind the wheel","content-positioning.subheadline":"Earn what you need","content-positioning.subheadline.commute":"Give a ride to a neighbor or coworker and save","content-positioning.subheadline.delivery":"partner with Uber","content-positioning.subheadline.intl":"Make as much money as you need","