nt.no.sign_up.no_amount":"Sign up with Uber and earn money by driving","endorsement.no.sign_up.no_amount.couriers":"Sign up with Uber and earn money by driving","endorsement.panels.good_driver.confirm":"I am a good driver","endorsement.panels.maybe_driver.confirm":"I might be a good driver","endorsement.sms.good_driver":"Is ${endorsee_first_name} a good driver?","endorsement.sms.tooltip":"Please provide your feedback for ${endorsee_first_name}","endorsement.yes.headline":"You rated ${endorsee_first_name} a good driver","endorsement.yes.headline.couriers":"You think ${endorsee_first_name} has good delivery skills","endorsement.yes.sign_up":"Get ${referral_amount} for signing up to drive with Uber","endorsement.yes.sign_up.couriers":"Get ${referral_amount} for signing up to drive with Uber","endorsement.yes.sign_up.no_amount":"Sign up with Uber and earn money by driving","endorsement.yes.sign_up.no_amount.couriers":"Sign up with Uber and earn money by driving","enterprise_logo.alt":"Enterprise company logo","error.500.message":"We're experiencing a technical issue, please try again in a few minutes.","error.internal-server-error-text":"We're experiencing a technical issue, please try again in a few minutes.","error.join-legacy.invalid-signup":"Please correct the following:","errors.commute-flow-switch-message":"It looks like you already have a driving account with Uber. To learn more about Commute, please contact \u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Ft.uber.com\u002Fcommutehelp\"\u003ECustomer Support\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","errors.partner-not-eligible-for-commute":"It looks like you already have a driving account with Uber. To learn more about Commute, please contact \u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Ft.uber.com\u002Fcommutehelp\"\u003ECustomer Support\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","faq.activation_time.a":"The online signup process can be done in minutes. We will notify you via email once your documents have been approved.","faq.activation_time.q":"How long does it take to get activated?","faq.fares.a":"\u003Cp\u003EThe trip fare you see at the end of a ride is calculated by adding:\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003Ebase fare: the price for pickup\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Etime: from start to end of trip\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Edistance: miles or kilometers of route\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Esurge pricing (if applicable)\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Etolls (if applicable)\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003C\u002Ful\u003EThis amount is charged to the rider.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EYour payment for the trip is calculated as: \u003Cbr\u002F\u003E((base fare + time rate + distance rate) * surge multiplier) - Uber fee + tolls.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003ETime and distance rates will differ depending on the vehicle option that you drive (uberX, UberBLACK) and the city youre driving in.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","faq.fares.q":"How are fares calculated?","faq.find_drivers.a":"The options to get matched with local driver partners currently vary per city. Contact your local Uber team or visit your closest local Uber office to learn more about it once you have signed up. Stay tuned, new tools are coming soon!","faq.find_drivers.q":"Will you help me find drivers?","faq.fleet.heading":"\u003Ch4 class=\"secondary-font push-tiny--bottom\"\u003EFAQS\u003C\u002Fh4\u003E\n\u003Ch3 class=\"primary-font\"\u003EWhat to expect as a Fleet Partner?\u003C\u002Fh3\u003E","faq.heading":"\u003Cspan class='primary-font'\u003EHave questions?\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EWe have answers.","faq.how_uber_works.a":"\u003Cp\u003EUber is a technology platform with apps that connect driver-partners and riders. As a driver-partner, you use your own vehicle to pick up riders and drive them to destinations in your city.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EYou receive a fare for each trip. At the end of each week, your total payment is sent by direct deposit to your banking account.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","faq.how_uber_works.q":"How does Uber work?","faq.link":"Read FAQs","faq.payment.a":"\u003Cp\u003EEvery week, your trip fares are totaled and paid to you as a direct deposit to your bank account. When getting started as a driver-partner, you can connect your checking account to your Uber account to receive all payments on time.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EIf youre affiliated with a Fleet Partner, this person receives your weekly payments.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","faq.payment.q":"How are driver-partners paid?","faq.rejected_documents.a":"The reason behind the rejection of each of your wrong documents will be notified to you via email.","faq.rejected_documents.q":"Why are my documents rejected?","faq.requirements.a":"\u003Cp\u003ETo become a driver-partner with Uber, you must:\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003Ebe at least 21 years old\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Ehave at least one year of driving experience in the U.S. \u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Ehave at least 3 years of driving experience if youre under 23\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Euse an eligible 4-door vehicle made in 2001 or later\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Euse an iPhone 4S or newer, or Android device running 4.0 or newer\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003C\u002Ful\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EYou must also upload:\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003Eyour valid U.S. drivers license\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Eproof of vehicle registration\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003Eproof of insurance for the vehicle listed on your account\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003C\u002Ful\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","faq.requirements.q":"What are the requirements to become an Uber driver-partner?","faq.tips.a":"\u003Cp\u003EPart of the Uber experience is not having to exchange payment at the end of the ride. We never want riders to feel obligated to pay extra at the end of Uber trips.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EAlthough tipping is not required and the rider app does not include an option to tip, you are welcome to accept cash tips when riders offer.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","faq.tips.q":"Can driver-partners accept tips?","faq.vehicle_requirements.a":"You can start with as low as one vehicle and one driver and there is no maximum.\nFind all specific vehicle requirements \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fhelp.uber.com\u002Fh\u002Fe16fcb84-8322-4c17-8ece-e4b31e785992\"\u003Ehere\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","faq.vehicle_requirements.q":"How many vehicles and drivers should I have to sign up and what are the vehicles requirements?","fleet.about-content.content":"As a Fleet Partner with Uber, get your vehicles driven by driver partners you connect with via Uber and manage your earnings online.","fleet.about-content.content-positioning.header":"Why partner with Uber?","fleet.about-content.header":"Fleet Partners","fleet.about-content.header.secondary":"About","free_ride.driver_referral_button":"Sign up now","free_ride.driver_referral_button_v2":"Sign up to drive","free_ride.driver_referral_msg":"Get {reward_amount} for signing up to drive with Uber.","free_ride.driver_referral_msg_no_amount":"Sign up with Uber and earn money by driving.","free_ride.driver_referral_title":"Join {inviter_first_name} and get {reward_amount}","free_ride.driver_referral_title_no_amount":"Join {inviter_first_name}","free_ride.driver_referral_title_v2":"{reward_amount} reward","fuel_cards.remember_to_drive":"Remember, to keep your Fuel Card status active, you must complete 200 trips every month.","fuel_cards.what_if_dont_drive_enough_description":"If you dont meet the required trip minimum at the end of a month, your card may temporarily be placed on hold for the next month until you reach your monthly trip goal again.","fuel_cards.what_if_dont_drive_enough_title":"What if I don't complete the monthly trip requirement?","global_signup.already_driver":"Already a driver?","global_signup.becoming_a_driver":"Becoming a Driver","global_signup.landing.become_driver":"Ready to become a driver?","global_signup.landing.drivers":"Drivers","global_signup.landing.drivers_body":"Accept trips using the Uber app for drivers and get paid automatically.","global_signup.landing.faq.drive_own_car":"Can I drive my own car?","global_signup.landing.faq.drive_own_car_body":"Absolutely. In many cities where Uber is available, drivers have the option of using their personal car to provide rides and earn income.","global_signup.landing.faq.drive_smartphone":"Do I need a smartphone?","global_signup.landing.faq.drive_smartphone_body":"Not at all, weve got you covered!  When youre ready to start driving, Uber will have a smartphone ready for you, pre-loaded with the Uber app for drivers. Youll be earning income in no time.","global_signup.landing.faq.drive_whenever":"Can I drive whenever I want?","global_signup.landing.faq.drive_whenever_body":"Uber gives you the power to manage your own schedule. When youre available to offer rides, simply get on the road and start accepting requests. When you have other things to do, go offline until youre ready to drive again.","greenlight.city_not_found":"City not found. Please check the URL and try again.","greenlight.welcome":"Welcome to Uber ${city}","head.meta.description":"Sign up to drive with Uber","head.meta.title":"Sign up to drive with Uber","head.title":"Uber | Sign Up to Drive or Tap and Ride","hertz_logo.alt":"Hertz company logo","home.earnings.footnote":"\u003Cp\u003EEarnings are based on local net median hourly earnings of drivers in the previous month. Weekly and monthly earnings assume 40 hours per week and 4 weeks per month. \u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThis opportunity is for an independent contractor.  Actual earnings may vary depending on number of rides taken, time of day, location and other factors. \u003C\u002Fp\u003E","home.footnotes.instant-pay":"\u003Csup\u003E**\u003C\u002Fsup\u003EInstant Pay is not available everywhere.","home.hero.heading":"Drive with Uber","home.hero.heading.commute":"Drive to work?","home.hero.heading.delivery":"Deliver with Uber","home.hero.heading.fleet":"